text: East Fife F.C. is a football club which plays in Scotland. == Stadium == East Fife's original ground was Bayview Park, in Wellesley Road in the centre of Methil. Since 1998, home matches have been played at the new all-seated Bayview Stadium situated at the old Lower Methil docks, capacity . ==References== == Other websites == Category:Scottish football clubs Category:1903 establishments in Scotland
